  |material=mineral\n}}\n\nA '''small piece of unrefined mithril''' is a type of [[stone]] that appears in [[UnNetHack]]. It is made of [[mineral]] rather than [[mithril]], and appears as a '''silvery metal stone''' when [[Identification|unidentified]].\n\n==Generation==\nSmall pieces of unrefined mithril are not randomly generated.\n\n2 to 16 small pieces of unrefined mithril are generated buried on the first level of the [[Ruins of Moria]] branch.\n\n==Strategy==\nThe main significance of small pieces of unrefined mithril is to be sold: its base price is more than twice that of a [[dilithium crystal]]. It cannot be used to [[engrave]], similar to a soft gem.\n{{variant-343}}\n[[Category:UnNetHack gems]]"}